headline: China’s Factory Activity Grows Narrowly in November
summary: CHINA NEWS An official gauge of China’s manufacturing activity edged up, marking its second consecutive month of expansion after Beijing moved to stabilize economic growth. The manufacturing purchasing managers index came in at 50.
